Changelog

Removed ssWPI due to proprietary installation Paths and no program associations, I prefer the native
Program installer for each App. I don't understand why such a great tool has to change installers
to preferences of developer, when in fact a clean build, installation should be 100 percent native
default Application install, not a mess of iconed folders in arbitrary places.
Also ssWPI flagged as virus by many AV Software, I'm sure its clean but not good to have so many false
Positives in a build.
WPI added and All new Silents made  for it. No Cracked programs used.

WPI Due to Developer not updating it I had to set half the Apps in Application Catagory due to WPI Bugs.
Installer is flawless but making it is difficult due to many bugs.

Ashampoo Latest Burning Studio added Pre-Regged, it creates 2 desktop shortcuts for its silly promotions
just delete them, as program is good in itself.

Changed reboot countdown time to allow for fast Computers to finish transformations


Below is the list of all new apps made today so some will be the same some different than last build minus
the ssWPI mess Leftovers.
